    {
      "type": "block-update-html",
      "pageId": "fa053582-3042-4fff-8130-d6c53563716d",
      "blockId": "84209a85-bcc6-4f6b-bf4e-b74af56c79b0",
      "html": "<header><h1 class=\"page-title\" dir=\"auto\" style=\"letter-spacing: -0.01em; line-height: 1.2; margin-bottom: 0.75em; font-size: 2.5rem;\">Knowledge.</h1><p class=\"page-description\" dir=\"auto\" style=\"margin-top: 0.5em; margin-bottom: 2em;\"></p></header><div class=\"page-body\"><div dir=\"auto\" style=\"color: rgb(55, 53, 47); font-family: ui-sans-serif, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI Variable Display&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Noto Sans Arabic&quot;, &quot;Noto Sans Hebrew&quot;, Arial, sans-serif, &quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;; font-size: medium; white-space-collapse: preserve; display: contents;\"><h3 id=\"301ba89f-2f77-804d-b1ba-e5397ae7c005\" class=\"\" style=\"letter-spacing: -0.01em; line-height: 1.2; font-size: 1.25rem; margin-top: 1.25rem;\">Overview.</h3></div><div dir=\"auto\" style=\"color: rgb(55, 53, 47); font-family: ui-sans-serif, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI Variable Display&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Noto Sans Arabic&quot;, &quot;Noto Sans Hebrew&quot;, Arial, sans-serif, &quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;; font-size: medium; white-space-collapse: preserve; display: contents;\"><p id=\"301ba89f-2f77-807e-8fda-c246032a7bb2\" class=\"\" style=\"margin-top: 0.5em; margin-bottom: 0.5em;\">DNA is a double helix. 2 strands</p></div><div dir=\"auto\" style=\"color: rgb(55, 53, 47); font-family: ui-sans-serif, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI Variable Display&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Noto Sans Arabic&quot;, &quot;Noto Sans Hebrew&quot;, Arial, sans-serif, &quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;; font-size: medium; white-space-collapse: preserve; display: contents;\"><p id=\"301ba89f-2f77-80d8-9ce1-c487cb6b0247\" class=\"\" style=\"margin-top: 0.5em; margin-bottom: 0.5em;\">Each strand is a chain of nucleotides</p></div><div dir=\"auto\" style=\"color: rgb(55, 53, 47); font-family: ui-sans-serif, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI Variable Display&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Noto Sans Arabic&quot;, &quot;Noto Sans Hebrew&quot;, Arial, sans-serif, &quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;; font-size: medium; white-space-collapse: preserve; display: contents;\"><p id=\"301ba89f-2f77-8033-9213-e93d55c73fa2\" class=\"\" style=\"margin-top: 0.5em; margin-bottom: 0.5em;\">At each position, 2 bases interact forming a base pair - ie. A and G</p></div><div dir=\"auto\" style=\"color: rgb(55, 53, 47); font-family: ui-sans-serif, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI Variable Display&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Noto Sans Arabic&quot;, &quot;Noto Sans Hebrew&quot;, Arial, sans-serif, &quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;; font-size: medium; white-space-collapse: preserve; display: contents;\"><p id=\"301ba89f-2f77-801c-8c1c-dbed04467871\" class=\"\" style=\"margin-top: 0.5em; margin-bottom: 0.5em;\">\n</p></div><div dir=\"auto\" style=\"color: rgb(55, 53, 47); font-family: ui-sans-serif, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI Variable Display&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Noto Sans Arabic&quot;, &quot;Noto Sans Hebrew&quot;, Arial, sans-serif, &quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;; font-size: medium; white-space-collapse: preserve; display: contents;\"><p id=\"301ba89f-2f77-80d8-879d-ec9e433068ee\" class=\"\" style=\"margin-top: 0.5em; margin-bottom: 0.5em;\">A nucleotide has one base (A/C/G/T) and a sugar/phosphate chemistry to keep it together.</p></div><div dir=\"auto\" style=\"color: rgb(55, 53, 47); font-family: ui-sans-serif, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI Variable Display&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Noto Sans Arabic&quot;, &quot;Noto Sans Hebrew&quot;, Arial, sans-serif, &quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;; font-size: medium; white-space-collapse: preserve; display: contents;\"><p id=\"301ba89f-2f77-8099-a5de-fb4b94a01f19\" class=\"\" style=\"margin-top: 0.5em; margin-bottom: 0.5em;\">\n</p></div><div dir=\"auto\" style=\"color: rgb(55, 53, 47); font-family: ui-sans-serif, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI Variable Display&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Noto Sans Arabic&quot;, &quot;Noto Sans Hebrew&quot;, Arial, sans-serif, &quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;; font-size: medium; white-space-collapse: preserve; display: contents;\"><p id=\"301ba89f-2f77-8020-94e3-e05b8bcb9c34\" class=\"\" style=\"margin-top: 0.5em; margin-bottom: 0.5em;\">groups of 3 bases are referred to as a <strong>codon</strong></p></div><div dir=\"auto\" style=\"color: rgb(55, 53, 47); font-family: ui-sans-serif, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI Variable Display&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Noto Sans Arabic&quot;, &quot;Noto Sans Hebrew&quot;, Arial, sans-serif, &quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;; font-size: medium; white-space-collapse: preserve; display: contents;\"><p id=\"314ba89f-2f77-80c2-8d65-d210d30cfffa\" class=\"\" style=\"margin-top: 0.5em; margin-bottom: 0.5em;\">RNA polymerase reads DNA one base at a time. There is no triplet framing.</p></div><div dir=\"auto\" style=\"color: rgb(55, 53, 47); font-family: ui-sans-serif, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI Variable Display&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Noto Sans Arabic&quot;, &quot;Noto Sans Hebrew&quot;, Arial, sans-serif, &quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;; font-size: medium; white-space-collapse: preserve; display: contents;\"><p id=\"314ba89f-2f77-8090-b9d8-d76e207abdf3\" class=\"\" style=\"margin-top: 0.5em; margin-bottom: 0.5em;\">The ribosome reads mRNA in non-overlapping triplets. That is where codons function as codons.</p></div><div dir=\"auto\" style=\"color: rgb(55, 53, 47); font-family: ui-sans-serif, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI Variable Display&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Noto Sans Arabic&quot;, &quot;Noto Sans Hebrew&quot;, Arial, sans-serif, &quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;; font-size: medium; white-space-collapse: preserve; display: contents;\"><p id=\"301ba89f-2f77-8063-aa66-fc0bb6b54e7c\" class=\"\" style=\"margin-top: 0.5em; margin-bottom: 0.5em;\">\n</p></div><div dir=\"auto\" style=\"color: rgb(55, 53, 47); font-family: ui-sans-serif, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI Variable Display&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Noto Sans Arabic&quot;, &quot;Noto Sans Hebrew&quot;, Arial, sans-serif, &quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;; font-size: medium; white-space-collapse: preserve; display: contents;\"><p id=\"301ba89f-2f77-801d-9d8a-ed1ed3880006\" class=\"\" style=\"margin-top: 0.5em; margin-bottom: 0.5em;\">mRNA is then translated into a protein</p></div><div dir=\"auto\" style=\"color: rgb(55, 53, 47); font-family: ui-sans-serif, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI Variable Display&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Noto Sans Arabic&quot;, &quot;Noto Sans Hebrew&quot;, Arial, sans-serif, &quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;; font-size: medium; white-space-collapse: preserve; display: contents;\"><p id=\"301ba89f-2f77-80eb-95bb-ffd8478072c5\" class=\"\" style=\"margin-top: 0.5em; margin-bottom: 0.5em;\">Each codon (3x bases) maps to one amino acid or a stop codon (special token which signals the end of protein synthesis)</p></div><div dir=\"auto\" style=\"color: rgb(55, 53, 47); font-family: ui-sans-serif, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI Variable Display&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Noto Sans Arabic&quot;, &quot;Noto Sans Hebrew&quot;, Arial, sans-serif, &quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;; font-size: medium; white-space-collapse: preserve; display: contents;\"><p id=\"301ba89f-2f77-80c9-a87e-c0fea0de63ee\" class=\"\" style=\"margin-top: 0.5em; margin-bottom: 0.5em;\">The codons are chained together using peptide bonds</p></div><div dir=\"auto\" style=\"color: rgb(55, 53, 47); font-family: ui-sans-serif, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI Variable Display&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Noto Sans Arabic&quot;, &quot;Noto Sans Hebrew&quot;, Arial, sans-serif, &quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;; font-size: medium; white-space-collapse: preserve; display: contents;\"><p id=\"301ba89f-2f77-808c-9f79-e162d52d0612\" class=\"\" style=\"margin-top: 0.5em; margin-bottom: 0.5em;\">This forms a polypeptide chain</p></div><div dir=\"auto\" style=\"color: rgb(55, 53, 47); font-family: ui-sans-serif, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI Variable Display&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Noto Sans Arabic&quot;, &quot;Noto Sans Hebrew&quot;, Arial, sans-serif, &quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;; font-size: medium; white-space-collapse: preserve; display: contents;\"><p id=\"301ba89f-2f77-80ec-9355-d8b81c7036f3\" class=\"\" style=\"margin-top: 0.5em; margin-bottom: 0.5em;\">When the stop codon is encountered, the translation process stops</p></div><div dir=\"auto\" style=\"color: rgb(55, 53, 47); font-family: ui-sans-serif, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI Variable Display&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Noto Sans Arabic&quot;, &quot;Noto Sans Hebrew&quot;, Arial, sans-serif, &quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;; font-size: medium; white-space-collapse: preserve; display: contents;\"><p id=\"301ba89f-2f77-80d3-9335-e2317b49b708\" class=\"\" style=\"margin-top: 0.5em; margin-bottom: 0.5em;\">\n</p></div><div dir=\"auto\" style=\"color: rgb(55, 53, 47); font-family: ui-sans-serif, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI Variable Display&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Noto Sans Arabic&quot;, &quot;Noto Sans Hebrew&quot;, Arial, sans-serif, &quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;; font-size: medium; white-space-collapse: preserve; display: contents;\"><p id=\"301ba89f-2f77-8041-b8c6-d41d6cb4d628\" class=\"\" style=\"margin-top: 0.5em; margin-bottom: 0.5em;\">The polypeptide chain folds into a functional 3D structure (protein folding)</p></div><div dir=\"auto\" style=\"color: rgb(55, 53, 47); font-family: ui-sans-serif, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI Variable Display&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Noto Sans Arabic&quot;, &quot;Noto Sans Hebrew&quot;, Arial, sans-serif, &quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;; font-size: medium; white-space-collapse: preserve; display: contents;\"><p id=\"301ba89f-2f77-8055-8f80-da35a9e5118d\" class=\"\" style=\"margin-top: 0.5em; margin-bottom: 0.5em;\">This is referred to as its “native state” </p></div><div dir=\"auto\" style=\"color: rgb(55, 53, 47); font-family: ui-sans-serif, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI Variable Display&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Noto Sans Arabic&quot;, &quot;Noto Sans Hebrew&quot;, Arial, sans-serif, &quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;; font-size: medium; white-space-collapse: preserve; display: contents;\"><p id=\"301ba89f-2f77-808e-8e6e-ef734d614a43\" class=\"\" style=\"margin-top: 0.5em; margin-bottom: 0.5em;\">\n</p></div><div dir=\"auto\" style=\"color: rgb(55, 53, 47); font-family: ui-sans-serif, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI Variable Display&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Noto Sans Arabic&quot;, &quot;Noto Sans Hebrew&quot;, Arial, sans-serif, &quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;; font-size: medium; white-space-collapse: preserve; display: contents;\"><p id=\"301ba89f-2f77-800d-bf4f-e3236f45648c\" class=\"\" style=\"margin-top: 0.5em; margin-bottom: 0.5em;\">Degeneracy</p></div><div dir=\"auto\" style=\"color: rgb(55, 53, 47); font-family: ui-sans-serif, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI Variable Display&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Noto Sans Arabic&quot;, &quot;Noto Sans Hebrew&quot;, Arial, sans-serif, &quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;; font-size: medium; white-space-collapse: preserve; display: contents;\"><p id=\"301ba89f-2f77-80ce-ba4d-f2d5a19c7d65\" class=\"\" style=\"margin-top: 0.5em; margin-bottom: 0.5em;\">Codons are 3 nucleotides, each which have a base (A,C,G,T)</p></div><div dir=\"auto\" style=\"color: rgb(55, 53, 47); font-family: ui-sans-serif, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI Variable Display&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Noto Sans Arabic&quot;, &quot;Noto Sans Hebrew&quot;, Arial, sans-serif, &quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;; font-size: medium; white-space-collapse: preserve; display: contents;\"><p id=\"301ba89f-2f77-801d-9242-d944de4785af\" class=\"\" style=\"margin-top: 0.5em; margin-bottom: 0.5em;\">There are 64 possible triplet combinations (codons) using the four bases (A, U, G, C)</p></div><div dir=\"auto\" style=\"color: rgb(55, 53, 47); font-family: ui-sans-serif, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI Variable Display&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Noto Sans Arabic&quot;, &quot;Noto Sans Hebrew&quot;, Arial, sans-serif, &quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;; font-size: medium; white-space-collapse: preserve; display: contents;\"><p id=\"301ba89f-2f77-80b3-991d-f2fc1f9f0cc0\" class=\"\" style=\"margin-top: 0.5em; margin-bottom: 0.5em;\">Each codon encodes one amino acid</p></div><div dir=\"ltr\" style=\"color: rgb(55, 53, 47); font-family: ui-sans-serif, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI Variable Display&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Noto Sans Arabic&quot;, &quot;Noto Sans Hebrew&quot;, Arial, sans-serif, &quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;; font-size: medium; white-space-collapse: preserve; display: contents;\"><figure id=\"301ba89f-2f77-80b0-b98c-e20091c429aa\" class=\"image\" style=\"margin-top: 1.5em; margin-bottom: 1.5em; break-inside: avoid; border: none; border-radius: 0px; text-align: center;\"><a href=\"Knowledge/Screenshot_2026-02-08_at_4.55.20_PM.png\"><img src=\"Knowledge/Screenshot_2026-02-08_at_4.55.20_PM.png\" style=\"max-width: 100%; width: 709.984px;\"></a></figure></div><div dir=\"auto\" style=\"color: rgb(55, 53, 47); font-family: ui-sans-serif, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI Variable Display&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Noto Sans Arabic&quot;, &quot;Noto Sans Hebrew&quot;, Arial, sans-serif, &quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;; font-size: medium; white-space-collapse: preserve; display: contents;\"><p id=\"301ba89f-2f77-80e6-9449-d3ed01e5d0e9\" class=\"\" style=\"margin-top: 0.5em; margin-bottom: 0.5em;\">An amino acid can be encoded by multiple codons</p></div><div dir=\"auto\" style=\"color: rgb(55, 53, 47); font-family: ui-sans-serif, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI Variable Display&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Noto Sans Arabic&quot;, &quot;Noto Sans Hebrew&quot;, Arial, sans-serif, &quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;; font-size: medium; white-space-collapse: preserve; display: contents;\"><p id=\"301ba89f-2f77-8054-93ec-d7b092aa8fe8\" class=\"\" style=\"margin-top: 0.5em; margin-bottom: 0.5em;\">For instance, codons GAA and GAG both specify glutamic acid and exhibit redundancy</p></div><div dir=\"auto\" style=\"color: rgb(55, 53, 47); font-family: ui-sans-serif, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI Variable Display&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Noto Sans Arabic&quot;, &quot;Noto Sans Hebrew&quot;, Arial, sans-serif, &quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;; font-size: medium; white-space-collapse: preserve; display: contents;\"><p id=\"301ba89f-2f77-8080-b18c-d050b5494f65\" class=\"\" style=\"margin-top: 0.5em; margin-bottom: 0.5em;\">This is referred to as degeneracy</p></div><div dir=\"auto\" style=\"color: rgb(55, 53, 47); font-family: ui-sans-serif, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI Variable Display&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Noto Sans Arabic&quot;, &quot;Noto Sans Hebrew&quot;, Arial, sans-serif, &quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;; font-size: medium; white-space-collapse: preserve; display: contents;\"><p id=\"301ba89f-2f77-80df-b46f-c72ec48dd803\" class=\"\" style=\"margin-top: 0.5em; margin-bottom: 0.5em;\">Mathematically:</p></div><div dir=\"auto\" style=\"color: rgb(55, 53, 47); font-family: ui-sans-serif, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI Variable Display&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Noto Sans Arabic&quot;, &quot;Noto Sans Hebrew&quot;, Arial, sans-serif, &quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;; font-size: medium; white-space-collapse: preserve; display: contents;\"><p id=\"301ba89f-2f77-80b6-881a-cad4565bc8f9\" class=\"\" style=\"margin-top: 0.5em; margin-bottom: 0.5em;\">4^3 = 64 codons</p></div><div dir=\"auto\" style=\"color: rgb(55, 53, 47); font-family: ui-sans-serif, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI Variable Display&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Noto Sans Arabic&quot;, &quot;Noto Sans Hebrew&quot;, Arial, sans-serif, &quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;; font-size: medium; white-space-collapse: preserve; display: contents;\"><p id=\"301ba89f-2f77-80f8-ae04-f7382d6b70a9\" class=\"\" style=\"margin-top: 0.5em; margin-bottom: 0.5em;\">22 amino acids </p></div><div dir=\"auto\" style=\"color: rgb(55, 53, 47); font-family: ui-sans-serif, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI Variable Display&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Noto Sans Arabic&quot;, &quot;Noto Sans Hebrew&quot;, Arial, sans-serif, &quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;; font-size: medium; white-space-collapse: preserve; display: contents;\"><p id=\"301ba89f-2f77-8065-9c3d-f46d04c0b8e0\" class=\"\" style=\"margin-top: 0.5em; margin-bottom: 0.5em;\">\n</p></div><div dir=\"auto\" style=\"color: rgb(55, 53, 47); font-family: ui-sans-serif, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI Variable Display&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Noto Sans Arabic&quot;, &quot;Noto Sans Hebrew&quot;, Arial, sans-serif, &quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;; font-size: medium; white-space-collapse: preserve; display: contents;\"><p id=\"301ba89f-2f77-80e7-9967-fc5d39b9d4d3\" class=\"\" style=\"margin-top: 0.5em; margin-bottom: 0.5em;\">\n</p></div><div dir=\"ltr\" style=\"color: rgb(55, 53, 47); font-family: ui-sans-serif, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI Variable Display&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Noto Sans Arabic&quot;, &quot;Noto Sans Hebrew&quot;, Arial, sans-serif, &quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;; font-size: medium; white-space-collapse: preserve; display: contents;\"><figure id=\"301ba89f-2f77-802e-a8d9-fd37af038045\" class=\"image\" style=\"margin-top: 1.5em; margin-bottom: 1.5em; break-inside: avoid; border: none; border-radius: 0px; text-align: center;\"><a href=\"Knowledge/Screenshot_2026-02-08_at_4.33.13_PM.png\"><img src=\"Knowledge/Screenshot_2026-02-08_at_4.33.13_PM.png\" style=\"max-width: 100%; width: 668px;\"></a></figure></div><div dir=\"auto\" style=\"color: rgb(55, 53, 47); font-family: ui-sans-serif, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI Variable Display&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Noto Sans Arabic&quot;, &quot;Noto Sans Hebrew&quot;, Arial, sans-serif, &quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;; font-size: medium; white-space-collapse: preserve; display: contents;\"><p id=\"301ba89f-2f77-801b-946d-e9a2fa977f6a\" class=\"\" style=\"margin-top: 0.5em; margin-bottom: 0.5em;\">\n</p></div><div dir=\"auto\" style=\"color: rgb(55, 53, 47); font-family: ui-sans-serif, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI Variable Display&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Noto Sans Arabic&quot;, &quot;Noto Sans Hebrew&quot;, Arial, sans-serif, &quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;; font-size: medium; white-space-collapse: preserve; display: contents;\"><p id=\"301ba89f-2f77-809f-af89-dc678678be0b\" class=\"\" style=\"margin-top: 0.5em; margin-bottom: 0.5em;\">\n</p></div><div dir=\"auto\" style=\"color: rgb(55, 53, 47); font-family: ui-sans-serif, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI Variable Display&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Noto Sans Arabic&quot;, &quot;Noto Sans Hebrew&quot;, Arial, sans-serif, &quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;; font-size: medium; white-space-collapse: preserve; display: contents;\"><p id=\"301ba89f-2f77-803f-8071-d5fa3285b949\" class=\"\" style=\"margin-top: 0.5em; margin-bottom: 0.5em;\">respiration → ATP → powers RNA polymerase which moves along DNA → assembles RNA → ribosome grabs RNA → it steps along RNA and uses ATP to bring in amino acid and produce → peptide bond of amino acids → chain of amino acids together → folds into a protein → protein</p></div><div dir=\"auto\" style=\"color: rgb(55, 53, 47); font-family: ui-sans-serif, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI Variable Display&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Noto Sans Arabic&quot;, &quot;Noto Sans Hebrew&quot;, Arial, sans-serif, &quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;; font-size: medium; white-space-collapse: preserve; display: contents;\"><p id=\"301ba89f-2f77-80ba-b610-f3dda3e1a52e\" class=\"\" style=\"margin-top: 0.5em; margin-bottom: 0.5em;\">\n</p></div><div dir=\"auto\" style=\"color: rgb(55, 53, 47); font-family: ui-sans-serif, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI Variable Display&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Noto Sans Arabic&quot;, &quot;Noto Sans Hebrew&quot;, Arial, sans-serif, &quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;; font-size: medium; white-space-collapse: preserve; display: contents;\"><p id=\"301ba89f-2f77-80e4-8989-d6861770a36c\" class=\"\" style=\"margin-top: 0.5em; margin-bottom: 0.5em;\">DNA is a chemical polymer made of nucleotides.</p></div><div dir=\"auto\" style=\"color: rgb(55, 53, 47); font-family: ui-sans-serif, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI Variable Display&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Noto Sans Arabic&quot;, &quot;Noto Sans Hebrew&quot;, Arial, sans-serif, &quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;; font-size: medium; white-space-collapse: preserve; display: contents;\"><p id=\"301ba89f-2f77-8051-9fa9-e5d28235fd3b\" class=\"\" style=\"margin-top: 0.5em; margin-bottom: 0.5em;\">A nucleotide is one “letter” (A,C,G,T) plus sugar+phosphate (the chemistry).</p></div><div dir=\"auto\" style=\"color: rgb(55, 53, 47); font-family: ui-sans-serif, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI Variable Display&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Noto Sans Arabic&quot;, &quot;Noto Sans Hebrew&quot;, Arial, sans-serif, &quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;; font-size: medium; white-space-collapse: preserve; display: contents;\"><p id=\"301ba89f-2f77-801b-b22f-da0cba7b9625\" class=\"\" style=\"margin-top: 0.5em; margin-bottom: 0.5em;\">DNA is usually double-stranded: two complementary letters bind (A–T, C–G).<br>One matched pair across the strands is a base pair.</p></div><div dir=\"auto\" style=\"color: rgb(55, 53, 47); font-family: ui-sans-serif, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI Variable Display&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Noto Sans Arabic&quot;, &quot;Noto Sans Hebrew&quot;, Arial, sans-serif, &quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;; font-size: medium; white-space-collapse: preserve; display: contents;\"><p id=\"301ba89f-2f77-80d5-bd0a-c79b0c9fe393\" class=\"\" style=\"margin-top: 0.5em; margin-bottom: 0.5em;\">A gene is a stretch of DNA letters.</p></div><div dir=\"auto\" style=\"color: rgb(55, 53, 47); font-family: ui-sans-serif, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI Variable Display&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Noto Sans Arabic&quot;, &quot;Noto Sans Hebrew&quot;, Arial, sans-serif, &quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;; font-size: medium; white-space-collapse: preserve; display: contents;\"><p id=\"301ba89f-2f77-802a-afdd-e75b971c1f83\" class=\"\" style=\"margin-top: 0.5em; margin-bottom: 0.5em;\">When expressed, DNA is read in groups of 3 nucleotides.<br>A 3-letter group is a codon.</p></div><div dir=\"auto\" style=\"color: rgb(55, 53, 47); font-family: ui-sans-serif, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI Variable Display&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Noto Sans Arabic&quot;, &quot;Noto Sans Hebrew&quot;, Arial, sans-serif, &quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;; font-size: medium; white-space-collapse: preserve; display: contents;\"><p id=\"301ba89f-2f77-80f1-88a9-d9c420094312\" class=\"\" style=\"margin-top: 0.5em; margin-bottom: 0.5em;\">Each codon maps to one amino acid (or stop).</p></div><div dir=\"auto\" style=\"color: rgb(55, 53, 47); font-family: ui-sans-serif, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI Variable Display&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Noto Sans Arabic&quot;, &quot;Noto Sans Hebrew&quot;, Arial, sans-serif, &quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;; font-size: medium; white-space-collapse: preserve; display: contents;\"><p id=\"301ba89f-2f77-80a9-8283-f989bcf93848\" class=\"\" style=\"margin-top: 0.5em; margin-bottom: 0.5em;\">Amino acids are small chemicals (20 main types) that link into a chain.</p></div><div dir=\"auto\" style=\"color: rgb(55, 53, 47); font-family: ui-sans-serif, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI Variable Display&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Noto Sans Arabic&quot;, &quot;Noto Sans Hebrew&quot;, Arial, sans-serif, &quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;; font-size: medium; white-space-collapse: preserve; display: contents;\"><p id=\"301ba89f-2f77-802a-a597-fd78552157e1\" class=\"\" style=\"margin-top: 0.5em; margin-bottom: 0.5em;\">That amino-acid chain is a protein.</p></div><div dir=\"auto\" style=\"color: rgb(55, 53, 47); font-family: ui-sans-serif, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI Variable Display&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Noto Sans Arabic&quot;, &quot;Noto Sans Hebrew&quot;, Arial, sans-serif, &quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;; font-size: medium; white-space-collapse: preserve; display: contents;\"><p id=\"301ba89f-2f77-80bc-9d39-ee82c290f360\" class=\"\" style=\"margin-top: 0.5em; margin-bottom: 0.5em;\">So:<br>nucleotides → DNA sequence (base pairs in double helix) → codons (triplets) → amino acids → protein.</p></div><div dir=\"auto\" style=\"color: rgb(55, 53, 47); font-family: ui-sans-serif, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI Variable Display&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Noto Sans Arabic&quot;, &quot;Noto Sans Hebrew&quot;, Arial, sans-serif, &quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;; font-size: medium; white-space-collapse: preserve; display: contents;\"><p id=\"301ba89f-2f77-80d4-bb16-e4996edb93e9\" class=\"\" style=\"margin-top: 0.5em; margin-bottom: 0.5em;\">\n</p></div><div dir=\"auto\" style=\"color: rgb(55, 53, 47); font-family: ui-sans-serif, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI Variable Display&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Noto Sans Arabic&quot;, &quot;Noto Sans Hebrew&quot;, Arial, sans-serif, &quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;; font-size: medium; white-space-collapse: preserve; display: contents;\"></div></div>",
